Mistinguett https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mistinguett 0 Mistinguett (French: [mistɛ̃ɡɛt]; 3 April 1875 – 5 January 1956) was a French actress and singer, whose birth name was Jeanne Florentine Bourgeois. She was at one time the highest-paid female entertainer in the world.
